{"tid":2010004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兒子涉社運羈押半年 母親堅持每日探望：有着我便有着你","createTime":"2020-05-10T07:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T13:34:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f39d2ac74c5f0cb012cd06b9c9dbf60436366364","tid":2010004,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200510/7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200510%2F7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU%2F&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=00b283a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200510%2F7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU%2F&h=38f79941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200510/7U7DWN2QCZMYXIH77K23OOMTFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n每天早上，一般母親不是買餸，便是返工；但對於被捕人士，他們的母親每日走的，卻是一條不同的路。堅仔（化名）去年因反修例衝突被捕，還柙至今已逾半年，他的媽媽起初會盡量抽空，上班前先到荔枝角收押所探望兒子，自年初辭工後，更是每天早上準時探監。半年以來，眼見兒子如人球般被調來調去，曾因遭人針對而獨囚「水飯房」，及後又突然調倉到赤柱監獄，當中身心的痛，堅仔媽媽無法向外人道。不過，她仍堅持每日探望兒子，即使相隔一塊玻璃、一對聽筒，希望兒子仍感受母親的無限支持。<br />\n<br />\n她仍記得堅仔還柙初期的幾個月，精神憔悴、瘦了一圈，身為母親，見了當然好心痛，但她愛莫能助，「好想入面嗰個係自己」。"},{"pid":"136eaa214fa639a20929670e609bd5090a6146e5","tid":2010004,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"張學友"},{"pid":"55b5304e0f50aab64402e3d44c4119ebadd5b3ef","tid":2010004,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:03:52.000Z","msg":"多謝手足犧牲 一定要血債票償<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"0ac5ac3cf2250dbb09e437e6124c589ce42a5bee","tid":2010004,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},